window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Never tempt the devil...</b></p> <p>It should be easy: Avenge his family by destroying the daughter of the man who ruined his life.</p> <p>Lilith. The beautiful, spoiled Omega daughter of a monster.</p> <p>He wants to take her. Break her. End her.</p> <p>But she threatens to tear at his heart and melt the ice that has frozen his soul.</p> <p>Revenge should be simple. Yet his obsession with her is anything but.</p> <p>Alpha Villain<i> is a standalone dark M/F romance with Alpha, Beta, and Omega dynamics, with plenty of heats, knots, and ruts. Guaranteed HEA! For mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
